Package: lvm-snapshot-manager
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: MiniSixth <service@minisixth.com>
Depends: bash, lvm2, util-linux, coreutils, gawk, bc
Description: A comprehensive utility for managing LVM snapshots.
 A modular and robust command-line tool to create, restore, list,
 monitor, and delete LVM snapshots. It supports configuration files,
 multi-language output, and health checks.